CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper November 17, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "On Parade - Sgt. William Carney Post, VFW, shown as they paraded Armistice Day. The Post is led by Commander Arthur S. Brown. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Armistice Day parade with group from Sgt. William Carney VFW Post led by Commander Arthur S. Brown, passing by Rosenbaum's department store, Liberty Avenue, Downtown
